@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = ((0.97 / 0.63) + 0.52)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin((tmp + 0.43 + v0 + 0.85)))
    tmp = (tmp - (0.01 + (tmp + 0.92 - v1 + 0.35)))
    v2 = wp.cos((v0 * wp.exp(v2 + 0.10)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.88))
    data[tid] = v0
